headline: Nvidia GTC, Tesla, Lululemon on TikTok: Market Minute
summary: Yahoo Finance host Brad Smith tracks several of the day's top trending stock tickers in this Market Minute. Nvidia (NVDA) kicks off its week-long 2025 GTC (GPU Technology Conference) event today, with CEO Jensen Huang to deliver a keynote speech on Tuesday, March 18. Mizuho analysts cut their price target on EV maker Tesla (TSLA). Lululemon Athletica (LULU) shares get a lift on after Truist analysts found it to be outperforming other brands in social media exposure on TikTok and other platforms. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
